{"id":5828,"date":"2024-02-21T12:41:56","date_gmt":"2020-02-21T07:11:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=5828"},"modified":"2024-02-13T17:38:13","modified_gmt":"2024-02-13T12:08:13","slug":"living-room-wall-shelves","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-wall-shelves\/","title":{"rendered":"Storage Made Easier With Wall Shelves For Your Living Room"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Organising can be real fun! Whether you are looking for more storage or plain decor wall shelves in your living room can add that extra oomph to your home. They are practical, occupy less space and are available in different shapes and sizes. And what\u2019s more, they are available in creative designs too, some of which are multipurpose in nature. You can use them to display your books, travel souvenirs, indoor plants and more \u2013 basically anything that will bring out the character of your home. Come let us take a sneak peek into various wall shelf designs for your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Wall Shelves For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are thinking of getting a wall shelf in your living room then consider wood. Wooden wall shelves ooze simplicity and charm that is typical of the countryside. They are a great choice if you want a rustic vibe in your living room. So, if you are seeking a clean and minimalist look opt for floating wooden shelves. You can combine it with some stained wood into the mix for effects.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_5837\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005302\/wall-shelves-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Wall shelves for living room is a great choice if you want a rustic vibe with a bookshelf design for living room\" class=\"wp-image-5837\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005302\/wall-shelves-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005302\/wall-shelves-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005302\/wall-shelves-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005302\/wall-shelves-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wooden shelves lend a look of comfort and elegance to living rooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Living Room With Glass Shelves<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn\u2019t love glass shelving? Glass is a transparent material that blends seamlessly into the environment for a light and airy feel to any room. You can custom design them or purchase glass shelves and hang them with brackets. Anything placed on a glass shelf takes centre stage. For instance, books placed on them appear to be floating. Knick-knacks placed on glass shelves visually stand out and can be admired from all angles. If you don\u2019t have wall space to mount shelves, opt for freestanding variety. Glass shelves have several advantages, especially with small homes, as they make a room feel less cluttered.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_5834\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005251\/living-room-glass-shelves-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Living room shelves where a transparent material that blends seamlessly into the environment for a light of glass shelves for living room\" class=\"wp-image-5834\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005251\/living-room-glass-shelves-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005251\/living-room-glass-shelves-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005251\/living-room-glass-shelves-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005251\/living-room-glass-shelves-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Glass shelves bring in character to your living room and make it appear spacious<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Looking for top home interior designers for your home?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09143614\/looking-for-top-home-interior-designers-for-your-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Multi-Tier Shelves For Your Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bare walls are not only to display artwork. What most homeowners do not realise is that they can be pretty useful. Bring in a touch of individuality to your living room with a multi-tier shelf. Multi-tier shelves in your living room, actually create an impression of space. This type increases the storage possibilities of bare walls. These are ideal if you have more to display or store.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_5838\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005306\/wooden-wall-shelves-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden wall shelves for living room where most homeowners do not realise is that they can be pretty useful as a wall shelves design for living room\" class=\"wp-image-5838\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005306\/wooden-wall-shelves-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005306\/wooden-wall-shelves-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005306\/wooden-wall-shelves-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005306\/wooden-wall-shelves-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A multi-tier corner shelf is a great way to flaunt decoratives and make use of bare walls<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Love Minimalism? Rectangular Shelves Are The Way To Go<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Minimalism doesn\u2019t get simpler than this! Rectangle shelves are a great way to showcase all your precious knick-knacks. Solid, wide frames with enough depth inside give you adequate space to store things. They are available in a variety of sizes, designs and colours so choose one that blends with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/\">interiors of your living room.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_5836\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005258\/shelves-design-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Shelves design for living room which are a great way to showcase all your precious knick-knacks with these cool wall shelf ideas for living room\" class=\"wp-image-5836\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005258\/shelves-design-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005258\/shelves-design-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005258\/shelves-design-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005258\/shelves-design-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Neutral rectangle shelves adds simplicity to spaces<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Adorn Your Wall With A Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You don\u2019t need to be a bookworm to have a bookshelf in your living room. A bookshelf is a great option to stack magazines, travel books, or even decor items. Put up those trophies, picture frames or pretty potted plants you want to see every day. A well-done bookshelf can be a lively addition to any living room.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_5830\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005235\/corner-shelf-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Corner shelf for living room where a bookshelf is a great option to stack magazines on wooden shelves for living room\" class=\"wp-image-5830\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005235\/corner-shelf-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005235\/corner-shelf-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005235\/corner-shelf-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005235\/corner-shelf-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Books and magazines make for great decor too so display them on a shelf<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-wall-decor-ideas\/\">10 Brilliant Living Room Wall Decor Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Beautiful Mess \u2013 Hexagonal Shelves For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hexagonal shelves are quirky and fun to have around and look like an ornament on your living room walls. This type of shelf design adds a striking feature to spaces. Mount it along the staircase wall and display all your favourite memorabilia. Knick-knacks, small plants or books stand out when placed here.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_5831\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005240\/decorative-wall-shelves-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Decorative wall shelves for living room where this type of shelf design adds a striking feature to spaces for living room shelf decor\" class=\"wp-image-5831\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005240\/decorative-wall-shelves-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005240\/decorative-wall-shelves-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005240\/decorative-wall-shelves-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005240\/decorative-wall-shelves-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Displaying your favourite items on hexagonal shelves looks fantastic<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Wall shelves zing up living rooms. Our list here gives you a wide range of possibilities to deck up those walls for&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">stylish home interiors<\/a>. Choose one because it stays with you for years to come!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/floating-wall-shelves\/\">11 Inspiring Ways to Elevate Your Floating Shelves<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/wallpaper-designs-for-living-room\/\">Wallpaper Designs For Your Living Room<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n      